    • GlowMetaKnowledgeBook

      public GlowMetaKnowledgeBook​(org.bukkit.inventory.meta.ItemMeta meta)
      Creates an instance by copying from the given ItemMeta. If that item is another KnowledgeBookMeta, its recipes are copied; otherwise, the new book is empty.
      Parameters:
      meta - the ItemMeta to copy
